(Pop) and Ramon de Ocampo (Luis).  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   `ALIEN BOY'
</P>
<P>
   By Will Scheffer; directed by Mark Roberts.  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   With: David Greenspan (Alien Boy).  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   `PROOF'
</P>
<P>
   By Jeff Reich; directed by Kevin Confoy. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   With: Forest Compton (Norman P. Carver) and Brad Bellamy (Nathan
Simpson). &QL;
</P>
