BKN-LAKERS-BLAZERS (Los Angeles) _ The Los Angeles Lakers face the
Portland Trail Blazers in Game 7 of the Western Conference finals
at 4:30 p.m. PDT. 
By Howard Beck. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BKN-CROUSE-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Column from Lakers-Blazers game. 
By Karen Crouse. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
