stand against gang members outside his suburban apartment complex,
and paid a heavy price: A shotgun blast took off his fingers and
ended his career. Now recovering in the hospital, he reportedly
fears retaliation, but is convinced he did the right thing. By Lisa
Van Proyen. (Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California
